    <h1 align = center> DAY 1 OF HTML</h1>

    <p>Hello this is my first webpage</p>

    <p>Here I'll show you the use of lists: </p>
    <ol>
      <li>Fruits</li>
      <li>Veggies</li>
    </ol>

    <p>Now let us see unordered lists: </p>
    <ul>
      <li>fruits</li>
      <li>veggies</li>
    </ul>

    <p>and now description lists: </p>
    <dl class="Fruits">
      <dt>Mango: </dt><dd>Yellow fruits</dd>
      <dt>Apple: </dt><dd>Red fruits</dd>
    </dl>
    <p>Lets try nested lists now: :P </p>
    <dl class="Eatables">
      <dt>Fruits: </dt>
      <dd>
        <ol>
          <li>Mango</li>
          <li>Apple</li>
          <li>Banana</li>
        </ol>
      </dd>
      <dt>Veggies: </dt>
      <dd>
        <ol>
          <li>Potato</li>
          <li>tomato</li>
        </ol>
      </dd>
    </dl>


    <p>This is sufficient for the day, I guess </p>
